<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1943-06-09T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-06-09T00:00:00-05:00" n="615" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d615">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">861.24/1526a</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss>
                                    to the Chargé of the Soviet Union</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Gromyko</hi></persName>)</head>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">
                                    <placeName>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-06-09">June 9,
                                    1943</date>.</dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">My Dear Mr. Chargé d’affaires</hi>: The
                                financing of the United States offerings, contained in the Proposed
                                Third Soviet Protocol, are contingent on the passage of the
                                Lend-Lease Appropriation Bill by the Congress. No difficulty is
                                expected to be encountered in the passage of the bill,<note n="1" xml:id="d615fn1">The bill, “Defense Aid Supplemental Act, 1943”,
                                    became law on June 14, 1943; 57 Stat. 151.</note> and it is
                                hoped to be able to inform you in the near future that the
                                appropriation legislation has been enacted.</p>
                            <p>Sincerely yours,</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed>[<hi rend="smallcaps">Cordell Hull</hi>]</signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>